data.title: A. J. Langer
data.meta_description: Allison Joy Langer, Countess of Devon, commonly known by her stage name A. J. Langer, is an American former actress. She is most known for playing Caroline Larkin in season two of Baywatch and as Rayanne Graff on the television series My So-Called Life.
